com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle

インタフェース PropertyResolver

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    PropertiesExpander

    public interface PropertyResolver
    Resolves properties in module configurations. The ConfigurationLoader uses a PropertyResolver to resolve the values of external properties like ${basename} that occur in the configuration file.
    作成者:
    lkuehne
    関連項目:
    ConfigurationLoader

    • メソッドの概要

      メソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      String resolve(String aName)
      Resolves a property name to it's value.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • resolve

        String resolve(String aName)
               throws CheckstyleException
        Resolves a property name to it's value.
        パラメータ:
        aName - the name of the property.
        戻り値:
        the value that is associated with propertyName.
        例外:
        CheckstyleException - if the propertyName cannot be reolved
